title: Picnic Time Topanga Insulated Cooler Tote, St. Tropez
description: This Picnic Time Topanga insulated cooler tote is the perfect all-around bag. It is made of durable polyester with complementing stitching accents to enhance its simple yet sophisticated lines. The interior lining is heat-sealed PVC, insuring no leaking, and its generous size will carry 24 soda cans. Perfect for carrying food and drinks to the beach or pool, this tote and features a separate exterior pocket that is the perfect size for your wallet or keys.  It can also be used to carry your wet swimsuits and towels on the trip home, and can double as a fabulous grocery bag.
